    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "END CREDIT\n\n---\n\nProject Team\n\nGroup Name: The brain is composed
    of 80% water\n\n Name: Thunyaphon Amphaphan\n Student ID: 1670704889 \n Section:
    229B No.22\n Role: UI, Programming\n\n Name: Thakrit Punyachaiwut\n Student ID:
    1670705191\n Section: 229B No.24\n Role: Game Design, Level Design\n\n Name:
    Sasipim Sayyot \n Student ID: 1670707163\n Section: 229B No.35\n Role: Assets,
    Testing\n\n---\n\nGame Description\n\nThis is a 2D platformer game where the
    player must survive through challenging levels filled with obstacles such as:\n\nFalling
    Platforms\nSaw Traps\nShooting Traps\n\n\nThe game applies several physics principles,
    including:\n\nUnity Physics 2D\nNewton's law of universal gravitation\nProjectile\n\n---\n\nAI
    Implementation\n\nThis project utilizes Generative AI tools to assist in game
    development, including concept generation and coding support.\n\n---\n\nAssets
    Credits\n\nMedieval Weapons & Tools Free Iron Set : https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/2d/environments/medieval-weapons-tools-free-iron-set-353788\nDungeon
    Platformer Tile Set (Pixel Art) : https://incolgames.itch.io/dungeon-platformer-tile-set-pixel-art\nDark
    Spell Effect : https://pimen.itch.io/dark-spell-effect\nMonsters Creatures Fantasy
    2 : https://luizmelo.itch.io/monsters-creatures-fantasy-2\n\"The Pale Moonlight\"
    tileset : https://corwin-zx.itch.io/the-pale-moonlight\nDungeon Asset : https://corwin-zx.itch.io/dungeon-tileset\nHeart
    pic : https://www.onlygfx.com/6-pixel-heart-png-transparent/\nBoldPixels Font
    : https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/2d/fonts/boldpixels-font-332078\n\n---\n\nSpecial
    Thanks\n\nCourse Instructor\nUnity Engine\nItch.io\n---\n\nThank You for Playing!\n"
